-- Bernanke to testify at House budget hearing Wednesday
-- 
-- Fri Jun 4, 2010 9:49am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/06/04/us-usa-fed-bernanke-hearing-idUSTRE65339G20100604

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - Federal Reserve Chairman Ben Bernanke will testify before the House Budget Committee on Wednesday, the Federal Reserve announced on Friday. 

 Bernanke will speak about economic and financial conditions, and the federal budget at a 10 a.m. EDT hearing titled "State of the Economy: View from the Federal Reserve." (Reporting by  Jasmin Melvin ; Editing by  Neil Stempleman )